latestIgtvVideos.title: Hair journey 🌻
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Got my hair done pretty at Jean Claude Biguine last week. I'd been wanting to get my hair colour evened out for a while but I let it be because I didn't want to torment my hair more than I already do at shoots. Also, no salon visits during the lockdown! The colorist at JCB helped me pick the shade I wanted and also gave me an olaplex treatment along with my color to nourish my damaged hair. The precautions they took made me feel comfortable sitting there for hours. The end result was exactly what I wanted! I loved going to JCB in Mumbai and now it's in Pune too 🤩 @jcb_kalyaninagar @jeanclaudebiguineindia
@olaplex

#JCBStyleMenu #JCBIndia #SafetyMeetsStyling

Thanks @simrantakawane from the JCB team for all the help

latestIgtvVideos.title: Majhi Kanya Bhagyashree
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
What you do is what matters, not what you think or say or plan. My journey so far has been great. No complaints, but there's still a long way to go for us to make our society a community in which girls and boys are treated at par. Girls need to be given the freedom to do what they love. 
I request you to watch and spread the word to someone who needs to know this.

Majhi Kanya Bhagyashree is an initiative by Maharashtra Govt. to further aid the Beti Bachao Beti Padhao mission.

Wearing an Ajrakh saree feels like draping art. The earthy tones and perfectly imperfect block prints have taken my heart away. You can sense the time and love poured into each piece- it’s not mass-produced, it’s made with intention. There’s a quiet power in its simplicity, and the kind of beauty that doesn’t scream for attention🦋
